Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:03.17,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:08.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:12.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:16.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.70,0:01:22.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.41,0:01:26.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:36.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:44.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.89,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:54.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:57.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:19.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:24.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:43.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:52.53,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:57.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:01.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:11.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:20.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:29.99,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:39.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:46.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:55.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:43.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:48.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:52.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:57.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:01.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:11.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:20.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:29.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:39.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:46.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:53.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.10,0:23:55.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
